com.b2international.commons.collections

Class IntSorter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.commons.collections.IntSorter

  • public class IntSorter
extends Object
    This class allows sorting int[] using a comparator without boxing elements to Integer. Simply override compare(int, int) to change sorting.
